      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The advertisement is written in Serbian Cyrillic letters and decoratively framed.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The roster in the upper left corner constitutes the logo of the French film producer ‘Pathé Frères’. The word ‘Frères’ is misspelt. The translation of the heading is: ‘Important for cinemas. The most famous producer of cinema pictures worldwide, Pathé Frère in Paris, has provided Svetozar Botorić, Belgrade, with its exclusive representation in Serbia and Bulgaria’.</ab>
